    <description>
HURL is a blazingly fast, user-friendly HTTP client written in Rust.

Features:
- Fast - Written in Rust for maximum performance
- Simple - Intuitive command-line interface  
- HTTP/1.1 &amp; HTTP/2 - Full protocol support
- Secure - Built-in SSL/TLS support
- JSON &amp; XML - Native data format support
- Colorized Output - Beautiful formatted responses
- History - Keep track of recent requests
- Assertions - Built-in testing capabilities
    </description>
